<font color="#ffff00">Luka memar.</font>

547
01:00:01,220 --> 01:00:03,420
<font color="#ffff00">Abrasi.</font>

548
01:00:04,360 --> 01:00:06,280
<font color="#ffff00">Patah tulang.</font>

549
01:00:07,280 --> 01:00:13,089
<font color="#ffff00">Menurut catatan medis, kau selalu dipukuli.
Apa itu benar?</font>

550
01:00:13,090 --> 01:00:21,500
<font color="#ffff00">Kesaksian Direktur Rumah Sakit Kim Seon Tae
mengonfirmasi bahwa kau mengalami patah tulang
